727548f-a.text:
Northern Boulevard, at the S.W. corner of Glenwood Street, at the Nassau County line, showing Harry S. Jobes' real estate office.  In the background are homes on Pembroke Avenue.  Glenwood Street, here, is the boundary between Queens and Nassau Counties.
P. L. Sperr
April 12, 1927
